"I-Nexus Imprint isebenzisa izigxivizo zeminwe ukuze ivuse iphinde ivule ifoni yakho, igunyaze ukuthenga, noma ingene ngemvume kuzinhlelo zokusebenza.
Qaphela ukuthi ungeza izigxivizo zeminwe zikabani. Noma iziphi izigxivizo zeminwe ezingeziwe zizokwazi ukwenza lezi zinto.
Yazi: Izigxivizo zakho zeminwe zingavikeleka kancane kunephethini enamandla noma iphinikhodi. "Funda kabanzi

"Nge-Pixel Imprint, ungasebenzisa izigxivizo zakho zeminwe ukuze ugunyaze ukuthenga noma ungene ngemvume kuzinhlelo zokusebenza.
Qaphela ukuthi ungeza izigxivizo zeminwe zikabani. Noma iziphi izigxivizo zeminwe ezingeziwe zizokwazi ukwenza lezi zinto.
Yazi: Awukwazi ukusebenzisa izigxivizo zakho zeminwe ukuze uvule le divayisi. Ukuze uthole olunye ulwazi, xhumana nomqondisi wenhlangano yakho."

"I-Nexus Imprint isebenzisa izigxivizo zakho zeminwe ukuze ivuse iphinde ivule ifoni yakho, igunyaze ukuthenga, noma ingene ngemvume kuzinhlelo zokusebenza.
Qaphela ukuthi ungeza izigxivizo zeminwe zikabani. Noma iziphi izigxivizo zeminwe ezingeziwe zizokwazi ukwenza lezi zinto.
Yazi: Izigxivizo zakho zeminwe zingavikeleka kancane kunephethini eqinile noma iphinikhodi."
Vele uthinte inzwa ye-Pixel Imprint ukuze uvuse uphinde uvule ifoni yakho.
Ngokungeziwe ekuvuleni ifoni yakho, ungaphinda usebenzise i-Pixel Imprint ukuze ugunyaze ukuthenga nokufinyelela kohlelo lokusebenza. Funda kabanzi
Khetha ukukhiya isikrini kwesipele ukuze usebenzise nge-Pixel Imprint
Nge-Pixel Imprint, ungavula ifoni yakho usebenzisa isigxivizo somunwe wakho. Ngokuphepha, le nketho idinga ukukhiya kwesikrini okuyisipele.
Uma isitoreji sesicishe sigcwele, susa izithombe ezenziwe isipele namavidiyo. Usengazithola Kuzithombe ze-Google.
Ukuze ushintshe ekungeneni nasekuphumeni kumodi yesithombe ozishuthe sona Kukhamera ye-Google, jikisa kabili uma ukuhlelo lokusebenza
Uma uxhumekile, usengafinyelela kuzithombe namavidiyo kukhwalithi oyikhethele ukuyenza isipele
